What you need to know:  The event, to be run on Sunday, will be based around Lisa Park in the outskirts of Machakos after the competition is flagged off from the People’s Park in Machakos at 8am in the morningKaran Patel, Motorsport Personality of the Year 2022, who is also the current Kenya National Rally Drivers Champion, is seeded at number one in his Ford FiestaPatel is followed by the Chana brothers Jasmeet  and Ravi in a Mitsubishi Lancer Evo10